d":2090330,"uid":53922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:05:39.000Z","msg":"舉報呢個日本仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:20:52.000Z","msg":"舉報百粉報好過啦"},{"pid":"7a98345b5f7f529ee427985c0192b2ccd3195013","tid":2090330,"uid":129664,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:22:27.000Z","msg":"日本最大問題係英文，希望可以加強返英語教學吧"},{"pid":"fc894bf773f29c7585e0c487c4d6d1c6c7a3f456","tid":2090330,"uid":67896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:22:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.co.jp/news/articles/2020-07-01/QCRY6BDWX2PT01\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.co.jp%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-07-01%2FQCRY6BDWX2PT01&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8MkuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=1db82082\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.co.jp/news/articles/2020-07-01/QCRY6BDWX2PT01</a><br />\n<br />\n貼返條Link先<br />\n<br />\n谷口崇子<br />\n2020年7月1日 17:46 JST<br />\n日本証券業協会の鈴木茂晴会長は１日の会見で、中国政府による香港の統制を強化する「香港国家安全維持法」が施行されたことに関して、「香港の金融の街としての地位は間違いなく失われていくだろう」と述べた。<br />\n<br />\n　　同法の施行によって、香港に高度な自治を認めた「一国二制度」の枠組みが見直され、これまでの自由な市場やビジネス環境が悪化するとの懸念が出ている。鈴木会長は、アジアの金融の中心がシンガポールなどにシフトする動きが加速する可能性があると指摘。一方、株式市場にすぐに影響が出るとは考えにくいとの見解も示した。"},{"pid":"8d57c76bb559a334513bc31375193369d83f9b6e","tid":2090330,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33142c6131af3d76a23d462d57a941389c6ea9aa","tid":2090330,"uid":28068,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"281dfeafa45700d67f790efeacd87047811797dc","tid":2090330,"uid":124439,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:02:58.000Z","msg":"日本仔黃金年代重臨,失落既十年應該會由香港同中國承擔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:19:41.000Z","msg":"十年?<br />\n三十年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:23:38.000Z","msg":"唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"